  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't remember exactly how many already got on But I and a friend of mine were standing on deck and we were the next one slated to go on one of the boats to be taken over.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of a sudden there was a loud explosion and the went down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In five minutes, it was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was lots of wreckage and lots of people swimming and trying to get away from the waves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a friend of mine who had a brother on the because the people from the other two boats, which I hadn't mentioned that there were other-- there were two other boats which came before us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- in Tulcea were three boats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One was the the other one was the and the third one was the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were three liners who waited for people like us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were two other transports who had come at the same time, one from Czechoslovakia on the and one from Vienna on the And so all together, the people who wanted to enter Palestine at that time numbered about 4,000.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that, which is very important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So those two boats, the the and the had arrived before us, because they didn't have any problems.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they already were on the Yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's very important.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were now supposed to be added to those people on the So the sank.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
